    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title">
                <app>
                    
                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"><app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #M">Index XXXV.</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXXIIII.</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXXIV. de Casimiro Polonorum regis
                                    filio a rebellibus in Hungariam introducto et a <app>
                                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S3">Matthia</rdg>
                                        <rdg wit="#S2">Mathia</rdg>
                                    </app> profligato</rdg>
                            </app></lem>
                    <rdg wit="#B"/>
                </app>
                </head>
                <p>
                <app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">
                        <s n="1">﻿<app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                            </app> dum animum intendit ad res novi regni ordinandas, solita rerum
                            humanarum fortunae mobilitas perturbare omnia <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #S1 #S2 #M">coepit</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">caepit</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#S3">cepit</rdg>
                            </app>, magnaque ex parte <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">eius</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#M"/>
                            </app> obfuit consilio.</s>
                        <s n="2">Nonnulli namque ex Hungariae primoribus prosperis <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthiae</rdg>
                            </app> invidentes successibus res moliti sunt novas, quae huiusmodi
                            fuere, ut, dum ipse <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">moraretur</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L1">moratetur</rdg>
                            </app> in Bohemia, regnum ei adimeretur Hungariae.</s>
                        <s n="3">Talium consiliorum principes fuere Ioannes Strigoniensis
                            archiepiscopus et Ioannes episcopus Quinqueecclesiensis.</s>
                        <s n="4">Erant hi natione Dalmatae humillimo loco nati, de quibus <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">erat <app>
                                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                                    </app></lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Mathias erat</rdg>
                            </app> bene meritus, quippe qui fuerat auctor, ut illi ad eas
                            praesulatuum dignitates eveherentur.</s>
                        <s n="5">Regiam igitur beneficentiam nonnisi maxima <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ingratitudine</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#L2">ingratudine</rdg>
                            </app> compensavere.</s>
                        <s n="6">Hi Poloniae regis filium Casimirum nomine cum multis Polonorum
                            legionibus in Hungariam intromiserunt, ac ante omnia Nitriensem arcem
                            loci natura armisque munitissimam illius potestati tradiderunt.</s>
                        <s n="7">Id ubi rescivit <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                            </app>, relicta Bohemia advolat in Hungariam, ipsumque Casimirum manu
                            valida obsidet, quem oppugnando eo ad extremum perduxit, ut desperans
                            ille locum se posse tueri ulterius, nocte inde egressus <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">profugerit</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">perfugerit</rdg>
                            </app>.</s>
                    </lem>
                    <rdg wit="#B"/>
                </app>
                <s n="8"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ea re cognita <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                            </app></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Polonorum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">-rum<note type="critic">B foll. 2 anteriora deperdita
                                sunt</note></rdg>
                    </app> copias et eas, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> tutatae fuerant arcem, et alias omnes, quae alia complura per Hungariae
                    fines occupaverant loca, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1">adorsus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #S3 #M">adortus</rdg>
                    </app> est, deque ea gente cladem edidit miserabilem.</s>
                <s n="9">Ex proceribus, qui capti sunt, multos misit ad urbem Budam, quo tam
                    celebrem adeptum se fuisse victoriam illorum captivitate suis ostenderet
                    popularibus.</s>
                <s n="10">Copiarum postea magnam partem misit, qui Poloniam omnibus, quibus fieri
                    posset, modis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">popularent</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">popularentur</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="11">At vero cum ei esset <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S3">nunciatum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #M">nuntiatum</rdg>
                    </app> Casimirum Polonorum regem in regione, quam appellant <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">Sclesiam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Silesiam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Sylesiam</rdg>
                    </app>, parare <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">multa</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">multi</rdg>
                    </app> armatorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">milia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">millia</rdg>
                    </app> in suorum Hungarorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">exicium</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">exitium</rdg>
                    </app>, alterum cogit exercitum, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">Sclesiamque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Silesiamque</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Sylesiamque</rdg>
                    </app> ingressus quam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">celerrime</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">celerime</rdg>
                    </app> petit Vratislaviam, nec procul ab ea urbe castra metatur.</s>
                <s n="12">Quod ut primum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">accepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">accaepit</rdg>
                    </app> Polonus, dat operam, ut suus augeatur exercitus, accersitis cunctis, qui
                    valere poterant armis, ex subiectis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">suae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">sue</rdg>
                    </app> ditioni gentibus non modo Polonis sed <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">Rutenis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R">Rhutenis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ruthenis</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">quoque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">Litfanisque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Litvanisque</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Lithvanisque</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">ac</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">et</rdg>
                    </app> Tartaris, omnibus igitur ad rem gerendam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">comparatis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">eomparatis</rdg>
                    </app> adversus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathiam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthiam</rdg>
                    </app> Vratislaviam versus contendit.</s>
                <s n="13">Ad cuius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S2 #S3 #M">urbis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">urbi</rdg>
                    </app> agrum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S2 #S3 #M">ubi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">ubis</rdg>
                    </app> pervenit, composito agmine tantum confecit itineris, quantum fuit ei
                    visum non plus mille passuum intervalli inter suum et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #R #L2 #S2 #S3 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mathie</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #S1">Matthiae</rdg>
                    </app> exercitum interesse, itaque e conspectu castrorum illius sua castra ipse
                    locavit.</s>
                <s n="14">Magna quidem fuit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">hominis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">nominis</rdg>
                    </app> huius <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">audatia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">audacia</rdg>
                    </app>, sed nequaquam rem vel gessit vel confecit eo, quo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S1 #S2 #M">coepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">caepit</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">cepit</rdg>
                    </app>, animo, obfuit enim ei hoc maxime, quod <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quamquam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">quanquam</rdg>
                    </app> eius exercitus abundabat maiore armatorum multitudine, Hungari tamen
                    erant cum animo tum virtute longe superiores, quod ut intellexit Polonus, animo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">infractus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fractus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">confractus</rdg>
                    </app> non ausus est cum Hungaro conserere manus.</s>
                <s n="15">Id animadvertens <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> curam dat <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #L2 #M">compluribus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2">cumpluribus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">cum pluribus</rdg>
                    </app> e sui exercitus copiarum ducibus, ut a diversis partibus hostilia castra
                    adoriantur.</s>
                <s n="16">Ea iussa ubi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">illis</rdg>
                    </app> sunt executi, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Polonos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2"/>
                    </app> nihil tale suspicantes ingens invasit formido, multi namque ex illis, qui
                    egressi castris vim repellere voluerunt, caesi sunt, alii acceptis vulneribus
                    confugerunt ad castra, innumeri fere capti.</s>
                <s n="17">Ex quorum numero singulos, qui obscuri erant et generis et nominis, iussit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> signari in facie <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">notabili</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">notatabili</rdg>
                    </app> vulnere indeque donari libertate, ut reversi illi ad suos <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S3">Hungaricae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Hungariae</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">Hungarae</rdg>
                    </app> gentis in Polonos iras testificarentur.</s>
                <s n="18">Constituerant Poloni duobus in locis castra fossa valloque ac fortium
                    virorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">firmata</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M"/>
                    </app> praesidio hoc consilio, ut in illis primum exciperentur commeatus, qui ex
                    amicis comportabantur civitatibus, deinde vero militum adhibita custodia ad
                    regia castra tute conveherentur.</s>
                <s n="19">Prudentum plane virorum id <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fuisset</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">fuisse</rdg>
                    </app> consilium, si diligentius ab ipsis esset provisum, quale consilium <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quantaeque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">quanteque</rdg>
                    </app> essent vires hostis, adversus quem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ceperant</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #L2">caeperant</rdg>
                    </app> arma.</s>
                <s n="20">Ipse namque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> excellenti illa, qua praeditus erat, ingenii vi illorum solertiam irritam
                    fecit.</s>
                <s n="21">Nactus enim tempus ad hoc idoneum bina illa castra <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2">adorsus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">adortus</rdg>
                    </app> est, eaque diripuit ac delevit incendiis, utque hostem maiore concuteret
                    terrore, misit Stephanum cognomento de <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S2 #S3 #M">Zapolia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Zápolia</rdg>
                    </app> totius exercitus sui ducem, virum bellica virtute insignem cum quadam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">parte copiarum</lem>
                    </app>copiarum parte, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> tendens in Poloniam omnem regionem popularetur, et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">quicquid</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quidquid</rdg>
                    </app> ei fieret <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2">obvium</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">obviam</rdg>
                    </app>, igni ferroque absumeret.</s>
                <s n="22">Ea re effectum est, ut adductus Polonus rex in summa rerum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">desperatione</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">desperationem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">desperatioue</rdg>
                    </app> pacem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">petiverat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">petiveret</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">peteret</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">petiverit</rdg>
                    </app>, quam nequaquam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">abnuit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">obnuit</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="23">Ventum igitur ad colloquium, post multa autem ultro citroque dicta tandem
                    inter <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">utrumque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">utrunque</rdg>
                    </app> regem pax benigne atque honeste composita in hanc perseverat diem.</s>
                <s n="24">Habuit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> Polonum suosque omnes adeo liberaliter, ut nihil supra dici <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">facile</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2"/>
                    </app> posset, mirifice postea regem ipsum donatum a se <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathias</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthias</rdg>
                    </app> dimisit, ita summo ille affectus stupore in suum se regnum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">recepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">recaepit</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
            </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
